V chng ti
Trung tm thng tin hng nghip v nghin cu, ng dng tm l (CRISP) l n v thit k ng
dng trn in thoi Shinning Mind - ng dng cung cp thng tin v Sc khe tm thn.
Lch s v chng ti:
Nm 2007, Trung tm Thng tin v Hng nghip (SCUIO Service Commun Universitaire
d'Information, d'Orientation, et d'Insertion Professionnelle) c thnh lp ti Khoa S phm
(tn c ca trng i hc Gio dc), trong khun kh ca trng Ples Universitaires Franais.
Trn nn tng , Trung tm Thng tin Hng nghip, Nghin cu v ng dng Tm l
(CRISP) c thnh lp vo thng 6, 2009, trc thuc i hc Gio Dc, HQGHN.
S mnh ca chng ti:
- Thc y vic ng dng kin thc tm l gii quyt cc vn kh khn ca con ngi
cng nh pht trin tim nng ca mi c nhn trong hc tp, gio dc, sc khe v cng vic,
ngh nghip.
- Thc y nng cao hiu bit v sc khe tm thn cho cng ng.
Cc dch v ca chng ti
Cung cp dch v nh gi tm l (nh gi tr tu, cm xc, hnh vi, v.v.) v
thch ng nhng thang o tm l mi.
Pht trin cc chng trnh can thip, cung cp tr liu cho nhng vn lin
quan ti sc khe tm l cho tr em v tr v thnh nin
Pht trin cc m hnh tham vn v h tr tm l trong trng hc v cng ng
T ch Kha tp hun, bi dng lin quan ti nhng vn trc nghim tm l
(WISC, ASEBA, v.v.), tham vn tm l hc v gio dc,
Tham vn, tr liu tm l c nhn

Cht lng thng tin trn App:
- Thng tin v sc khe tm thn u chng ti c cp nht mi nht trn cc website uy tn nh:
www.nimh.nih.gov, www.apa.org, www.helpguide.org , www.nhs.uk,
- Ton b thng tin v sc khe tm thn trc khi c a vo app Shinning Mind u c i ng c
vn chuyn mn kim duyt.
